                ['day_ms' => 'Khamis', 'day_en' => 'Thursday', 'activities_ms' => ['Cuti Umum Tahun Baru Cina (CNY).'], 'activities_en' => ['Chinese New Year (CNY) Public Holiday.']],
                ['day_ms' => 'Jumaat', 'day_en' => 'Friday', 'activities_ms' => ['Menghantar UAT MyResearch.', 'Bahan: laptop, Microsoft Word, Google Docs.', 'Membuat Google Docs di Google Drive.', 'Memasukkan dokumen UAT ke dalam Google Docs.', 'Memberikan link kepada penyelia.', 'Memberitahu penyelia dokumen UAT sudah siap.'], 'activities_en' => ['Submitted UAT for MyResearch.', 'Tools: laptop, Microsoft Word, Google Docs.', 'Created Google Docs in Google Drive.', 'Uploaded UAT document into Google Docs.', 'Shared link with supervisor.', 'Informed supervisor that UAT document was ready.']],
            ], 'reflection_ms' => 'Minggu ini saya menyambung dan melengkapkan dokumen UAT MyResearch pada hari Isnin selepas memberitahu penyelia terdapat error. Hari Selasa hingga Khamis adalah cuti umum Tahun Baru Cina. Pada hari Jumaat, saya menghantar dokumen UAT yang telah disiapkan kepada penyelia melalui Google Docs. Saya mempelajari cara menggunakan Google Docs untuk perkongsian dokumen secara dalam talian dan cara berkomunikasi dengan penyelia mengenai status tugasan. Latihan minggu ini meningkatkan kemahiran saya dalam pengurusan dokumen digital dan komunikasi profesional dengan penyelia.', 'reflection_en' => 'This week I continued and completed the MyResearch UAT document on Monday after informing the supervisor about errors found. Tuesday to Thursday were Chinese New Year public holidays. On Friday, I submitted the completed UAT document to the supervisor via Google Docs. I learned how to use Google Docs for online document sharing and how to communicate with the supervisor regarding task status. This week\'s training improved my skills in digital document management and professional communication with the supervisor.'],
            ['title_ms' => 'MINGGU 7', 'title_en' => 'WEEK 7', 'start_date' => '2026-02-23', 'end_date' => '2026-02-27', 'topic_ms' => 'Pengurusan Data MyKendiri & Pengenalan Framework Laravel', 'topic_en' => 'MyKendiri Data Management & Introduction to Laravel Framework', 'days' => [
                ['day_ms' => 'Isnin', 'day_en' => 'Monday', 'activities_ms' => ['Memahami aliran sistem MyKendiri dan struktur logiknya.', 'Bahan: laptop, perisian MyKendiri.', 'Merujuk penyelia untuk penjelasan lanjut mengenai proses kerja sistem.', 'Berjaya memahami aliran sistem secara keseluruhan.'], 'activities_en' => ['Understanding the MyKendiri system flow and its logic.', 'Tools: laptop, MyKendiri software.', 'Consulted supervisor for further clarification on system processes.', 'Successfully understood the overall system flow.']],
                ['day_ms' => 'Selasa', 'day_en' => 'Tuesday', 'activities_ms' => ['Mengenalpasti dan memadam data bertindih dalam sistem MyKendiri.', 'Bahan: laptop, perisian MyKendiri.', 'Membangunkan fail Excel untuk memantau kemajuan pembersihan data.', 'Memastikan integriti data terpelihara dengan membuang rekod pendua.'], 'activities_en' => ['Identifying and deleting redundant data in MyKendiri system.', 'Tools: laptop, MyKendiri software.', 'Developed an Excel file to monitor data cleaning progress.', 'Ensured data integrity by removing duplicate records.']],
                ['day_ms' => 'Rabu', 'day_en' => 'Wednesday', 'activities_ms' => ['Menyambung proses pembersihan data bertindih daripada hari sebelumnya.', 'Bahan: laptop, perisian MyKendiri, Excel.', 'Mengemaskini status tugasan secara sistematik menggunakan Excel.', 'Berbincang dengan penyelia bagi mengatasi kekeliruan pengendalian data.', 'Menjejak kemajuan kerja supaya selari dengan garis masa.'], 'activities_en' => ['Continued the redundant data cleaning process from the previous day.', 'Tools: laptop, MyKendiri software, Excel.', 'Systematically updated task status using Excel.', 'Discussed with supervisor to resolve data handling confusion.', 'Tracked work progress to ensure alignment with the timeline.']],
                ['day_ms' => 'Khamis', 'day_en' => 'Thursday', 'activities_ms' => ['Menyiapkan dan memuat naik laporan pembersihan data ke Google Drive.', 'Bahan: laptop, Excel, Google Drive.', 'Menghantar pautan dokumen kepada penyelia untuk semakan akhir.', 'Mengesahkan ketepatan data bagi memastikan tugasan selesai dengan betul.'], 'activities_en' => ['Completed and uploaded the data cleaning report to Google Drive.', 'Tools: laptop, Excel, Google Drive.', 'Sent the document link to the supervisor for final review.', 'Verified data accuracy to ensure the task was completed correctly.']],
                ['day_ms' => 'Jumaat', 'day_en' => 'Friday', 'activities_ms' => ['Memulakan sesi pembelajaran asas framework Laravel.', 'Bahan: laptop, VS Code, GitLab.', 'Melaksanakan arahan Laravel seperti migrate dan db:seed.', 'Memahami konsep awal pembangunan web menggunakan seni bina MVC.'], 'activities_en' => ['Started learning the basics of the Laravel framework.', 'Tools: laptop, VS Code, GitLab.', 'Executed Laravel commands such as migrate and db:seed.', 'Understanding initial web development concepts using MVC architecture.']],
            ], 'reflection_ms' => 'Fokus utama aktiviti minggu ini adalah pengurusan data dalam sistem MyKendiri dan pengenalan kepada framework Laravel. Sepanjang empat hari pertama, saya menumpukan usaha kepada mengekalkan integriti pangkalan data dengan mengenalpasti serta memadam data bertindih. Proses ini diuruskan secara sistematik melalui Excel dan hasil kerja dikongsi melalui Google Drive untuk semakan penyelia. Pada hari terakhir, saya beralih kepada aspek teknikal pembangunan web dengan mempelajari arahan asas Laravel seperti migration dan seeding. Secara keseluruhan, saya telah meningkatkan kemahiran dalam pengurusan pangkalan data serta memahami langkah awal pembangunan sistem moden menggunakan seni bina MVC.', 'reflection_en' => 'This week\'s activities focused on two main areas: data management within the MyKendiri system and the introduction to Laravel framework. For the first four days, I concentrated on maintaining data integrity by identifying and removing redundant records. To manage this effectively, I implemented a tracking system using Excel and shared the final results via Google Drive for supervisor verification. On the final day, I shifted to technical development by learning core Laravel commands, including migrations and seeding. Overall, I have gained better insight into database management and the initial steps of modern web development using the MVC architecture.'],
            ['title_ms' => 'MINGGU 8', 'title_en' => 'WEEK 8', 'start_date' => '2026-03-02', 'end_date' => '2026-03-06', 'topic_ms' => 'Pembelajaran Framework Laravel: Migration, Seeder, Model, Controller & Route', 'topic_en' => 'Learning Laravel Framework: Migration, Seeder, Model, Controller & Route', 'days' => [
                ['day_ms' => 'Isnin', 'day_en' => 'Monday', 'activities_ms' => ['Mempelajari cara membina struktur pangkalan data menggunakan fungsi migration dalam Laravel.', 'Bahan: laptop, VS Code, GitLab.', 'Membuat migration untuk setiap jadual yang diperlukan.', 'Menjalankan migration bagi mewujudkan semua jadual dalam pangkalan data.'], 'activities_en' => ['Learning how to build database structure using Laravel migration.', 'Tools: laptop, VS Code, GitLab.', 'Created migration files for each required table.', 'Ran migrations to create all tables in the database.']],
                ['day_ms' => 'Selasa', 'day_en' => 'Tuesday', 'activities_ms' => ['Menyambung pembelajaran pembangunan web Laravel.', 'Bahan: laptop, VS Code, GitLab.', 'Membuat seeder untuk data contoh sistem.', 'Menjalankan seeder bagi memasukkan data ke dalam pangkalan data.'], 'activities_en' => ['Continued learning Laravel web development.', 'Tools: laptop, VS Code, GitLab.', 'Created seeders for sample system data.', 'Ran the seeder to insert data into the database.']],
                ['day_ms' => 'Rabu', 'day_en' => 'Wednesday', 'activities_ms' => ['Menyambung pembelajaran Laravel dengan fokus kepada model.', 'Bahan: laptop, VS Code, GitLab.', 'Membuat model untuk diintegrasikan dengan pangkalan data.', 'Mewujudkan model untuk semua jadual yang berkaitan.'], 'activities_en' => ['Continued Laravel learning with focus on models.', 'Tools: laptop, VS Code, GitLab.', 'Created models to be integrated with the database.', 'Built models for all related tables.']],
                ['day_ms' => 'Khamis', 'day_en' => 'Thursday', 'activities_ms' => ['Menyambung pembelajaran Laravel dengan fokus kepada controller.', 'Bahan: laptop, VS Code, GitLab.', 'Membuat controller untuk memanggil fungsi yang diperlukan.', 'Mewujudkan semua fungsi yang diperlukan dalam controller.'], 'activities_en' => ['Continued Laravel learning with focus on controllers.', 'Tools: laptop, VS Code, GitLab.', 'Created controllers to call the required functions.', 'Built all necessary functions within the controllers.']],
                ['day_ms' => 'Jumaat', 'day_en' => 'Friday', 'activities_ms' => ['Menyambung pembelajaran Laravel dengan fokus kepada routing.', 'Bahan: laptop, VS Code, GitLab.', 'Membuat route untuk semua controller yang diperlukan.', 'Mewujudkan route bagi setiap halaman web sistem.'], 'activities_en' => ['Continued Laravel learning with focus on routing.', 'Tools: laptop, VS Code, GitLab.', 'Created routes for all required controllers.', 'Built routes for every web page in the system.']],
            ], 'reflection_ms' => 'Minggu ini saya menyambung pembelajaran Framework Laravel secara praktikal bermula daripada penyediaan migration, seeder dan model. Saya juga membina controller untuk mengurus fungsi sistem serta menetapkan routing bagi menghubungkan setiap halaman web dengan betul. Saya berjaya menguasai cara membina struktur pangkalan data menggunakan migration dan memahami aliran data antara model, controller dan route. Selain itu, saya juga mempelajari teknik memasukkan data contoh secara automatik menggunakan fungsi seeder bagi tujuan pengujian sistem. Secara keseluruhan, saya dapat memahami proses pembangunan sistem web yang lebih tersusun dan mempercepatkan tempoh pembangunan menggunakan fungsi sedia ada dalam Laravel.', 'reflection_en' => 'This week I continued learning the Laravel framework practically, starting from the preparation of migrations, seeders, and models. I also built controllers to manage system functions and set up routing to properly connect each web page. I successfully mastered how to build a database structure using migrations and understood the data flow between models, controllers, and routes. Additionally, I learned the technique of automatically inserting sample data using the seeder function for system testing purposes. Overall, I gained a better understanding of a more structured web system development process and how to speed up development using built-in Laravel features.'],
            ['title_ms' => 'MINGGU 9', 'title_en' => 'WEEK 9', 'start_date' => '2026-03-09', 'end_date' => '2026-03-13', 'topic_ms' => 'Modul Reference projek laporan latihan industri, pengujian MySare & struktur pangkalan data Laravel', 'topic_en' => 'Industrial training report Reference module, MySare testing & Laravel database structure', 'days' => [
                ['day_ms' => 'Isnin', 'day_en' => 'Monday', 'activities_ms' => ['Sambung MC (cuti sakit).'], 'activities_en' => ['Continued medical leave (MC).']],
                ['day_ms' => 'Selasa', 'day_en' => 'Tuesday', 'activities_ms' => ['Pembuatan modul Reference bagi projek pembelajaran laporan latihan industri.', 'Bahan: laptop, VS Code, GitLab.', 'Menarik kod terkini daripada repositori rujukan (GitLab).', 'Menyediakan migration, seeder dan komponen sokongan untuk modul Reference.', 'Menyelesaikan percanggahan kod selepas tarikan Git dengan gabungan manual dan menyusun semula struktur fail supaya selari dengan versi terkini.'], 'activities_en' => ['Built the Reference module for the industrial training report learning project.', 'Tools: laptop, VS Code, GitLab.', 'Pulled the latest code from the reference repository on GitLab.', 'Prepared migrations, seeders and supporting components for the Reference module.', 'Resolved code conflicts after Git pull via manual merge and reorganised the file structure to match the latest version.']],
                ['day_ms' => 'Rabu', 'day_en' => 'Wednesday', 'activities_ms' => ['Pengujian sistem MySare.', 'Bahan: laptop, Google Drive, Excel, perisian MySare.', 'Memuat turun helaian Excel kemajuan ujian daripada penyelia.', 'Menjalankan ujian berdasarkan senarai ujian dalam Excel.', 'Merekod fungsi yang tidak berfungsi seperti dijangka dan melaporkan kepada penyelia untuk tindakan susulan.'], 'activities_en' => ['MySare system testing.', 'Tools: laptop, Google Drive, Excel, MySare software.', 'Downloaded the supervisor\'s progress tracking Excel sheet.', 'Executed tests based on the checklist in Excel.', 'Logged functions that did not behave as expected and reported them to the supervisor for follow-up.']],
                ['day_ms' => 'Khamis', 'day_en' => 'Thursday', 'activities_ms' => ['Sambungan pengujian MySare.', 'Bahan: laptop, Google Drive, Excel, perisian MySare.', 'Menyiapkan separuh kedua senarai ujian.', 'Melaporkan ralat teknikal pada beberapa modul kepada penyelia untuk semakan dan pembetulan kod.', 'Memaklumkan penyelia selepas keseluruhan senarai ujian siap untuk semakan.'], 'activities_en' => ['Continued MySare testing.', 'Tools: laptop, Google Drive, Excel, MySare software.', 'Completed the second half of the test list.', 'Reported technical errors in several modules to the supervisor for review and code fixes.', 'Notified the supervisor once the full test list was completed for verification.']],
                ['day_ms' => 'Jumaat', 'day_en' => 'Friday', 'activities_ms' => ['Sambung belajar Laravel untuk projek laporan latihan industri.', 'Bahan: laptop, VS Code, Git Bash, Laragon.', 'Menyediakan migration untuk jadual menu_role dan medan/kolum berkaitan menu_id mengikut keperluan pangkalan data.', 'Menyemak semula fail migration (jenis data, indeks) apabila `php artisan migrate` menunjukkan ralat struktur, kemudian menjalankan semula migrate selepas pembetulan.'], 'activities_en' => ['Continued Laravel learning for the industrial training report project.', 'Tools: laptop, VS Code, Git Bash, Laragon.', 'Created migrations for the menu_role table and menu-related identifiers as required by the schema.', 'Reviewed migration files (data types, keys) when `php artisan migrate` reported structure errors, then re-ran migrations after corrections.']],
            ], 'reflection_ms' => 'Minggu ini saya memfokuskan kepada pembangunan modul Reference untuk projek pembelajaran laporan latihan industri termasuk migration dan seeder, serta pengujian menyeluruh sistem MySare menggunakan senarai semak Excel daripada penyelia. Pengalaman menyelesaikan percanggahan kod dalam GitLab selepas git pull mengukuhkan kepentingan menarik kod dengan teratur sebelum memulakan tugasan baharu. Pengujian MySare mendedahkan kepentingan dokumentasi ralat secara sistematik untuk semakan penyelia. Pada hari Jumaat, saya meneruskan struktur pangkalan data Laravel untuk jadual menu_role dan perkaitan menu, serta memahami cara mengemas kini migration apabila berlakunya ralat. Secara keseluruhan, minggu ini meningkatkan ketelitian dalam pengujian, kemahiran kawalan versi, dan kefahaman struktur pangkalan data dalam pembangunan sistem.', 'reflection_en' => 'This week I focused on building the Reference module for the industrial training report learning project, including migrations and seeders, and on comprehensive MySare system testing using an Excel checklist from my supervisor. Resolving GitLab code conflicts after pulling updates reinforced the importance of a clean pull before starting new work. MySare testing highlighted how systematically logging defects supports supervisor review. On Friday I continued Laravel database work for the menu_role table and menu-related fields, and learned to adjust migrations when migrate errors occur. Overall, this week improved my attention to testing detail, version-control skills, and understanding of database structure in system development.'],
            ['title_ms' => 'MINGGU 10', 'title_en' => 'WEEK 10', 'start_date' => '2026-03-16', 'end_date' => '2026-03-20', 'topic_ms' => 'Projek laporan latihan industri: migration artikel & galeri, pangkalan data CMS/portal & modul Pentadbiran Portal', 'topic_en' => 'Industrial training report: article & gallery migrations, CMS/portal database & Portal Administration module', 'days' => [
                ['day_ms' => 'Isnin', 'day_en' => 'Monday', 'activities_ms' => ['Sambungan projek laporan latihan industri (migration).', 'Bahan: laptop, VS Code, Laragon.', 'Menyediakan fail migration untuk jadual portal_articles dan galleries serta melengkapkan struktur kolum.', 'Menjalankan `php artisan migrate` untuk mengemas kini pangkalan data.', 'Menyemak semula fail migration dan menjalankan `php artisan migrate:rollback` diikuti migrate semula apabila berlaku ralat jenis data.'], 'activities_en' => ['Continued the industrial training report project (migrations).', 'Tools: laptop, VS Code, Laragon.', 'Prepared migration files for the portal_articles and galleries tables and completed the column definitions.', 'Ran `php artisan migrate` to update the database.', 'Reviewed migration files and ran `php artisan migrate:rollback` followed by migrate again when a data-type error occurred.']],
                ['day_ms' => 'Selasa', 'day_en' => 'Tuesday', 'activities_ms' => ['Pembangunan sistem projek khas laporan akhir (laporan latihan industri).', 'Bahan: laptop, VS Code, Laragon.', 'Memulakan pembangunan menyeluruh sistem laporan latihan industri sebagai bahan pembentangan laporan akhir latihan industri.', 'Merancang struktur antaramuka utama (laman utama) dan merangka susun atur kandungan bagi menu utama seperti pengenalan, penghargaan dan lain-lain.', 'Menyelaras draf kandungan portal dengan bab-bab wajib dalam buku panduan laporan industri politeknik bagi memastikan aliran maklumat tersusun untuk penilai.'], 'activities_en' => ['Development of the special final-report system (industrial training report).', 'Tools: laptop, VS Code, Laragon.', 'Started full-stack development of the industrial training report system as material for the final industrial training report presentation.', 'Planned the main interface (homepage) structure and drafted content layout for key sections such as introduction and acknowledgement.', 'Aligned portal content drafts with mandatory chapters in the polytechnic industrial report guide to keep information flow clear for assessors.']],
                ['day_ms' => 'Rabu', 'day_en' => 'Wednesday', 'activities_ms' => ['Pembangunan pangkalan data CMS dan portal.', 'Bahan: laptop, VS Code, Laragon.', 'Membina pangkalan data MySQL untuk kegunaan CMS dan portal serta menyusun jadual simpanan.', 'Merangka skema pangkalan data yang efisien bagi menyelaraskan perkaitan jadual antara modul CMS dan paparan portal.'], 'activities_en' => ['CMS and portal database development.', 'Tools: laptop, VS Code, Laragon.', 'Built a MySQL database for the CMS and portal and organised storage tables.', 'Designed an efficient database schema to align relationships between CMS modules and the portal frontend.']],
                ['day_ms' => 'Khamis', 'day_en' => 'Thursday', 'activities_ms' => ['Pembangunan modul Pentadbiran Portal dalam CMS.', 'Bahan: laptop, VS Code, Laragon.', 'Membangunkan fungsi kawalan pentadbiran portal dalam CMS.', 'Menyediakan antaramuka pengurusan untuk sub-menu Menus, Articles dan Media.', 'Melakukan konfigurasi routing Laravel bagi menyelaraskan pautan navigasi antara CMS dan portal serta memastikan capaian data tepat.'], 'activities_en' => ['Portal Administration module development within the CMS.', 'Tools: laptop, VS Code, Laragon.', 'Implemented portal administration controls inside the CMS.', 'Built management interfaces for the Menus, Articles, and Media sub-menus.', 'Configured Laravel routing to align CMS navigation with the public portal and ensure correct data access.']],
                ['day_ms' => 'Jumaat', 'day_en' => 'Friday', 'activities_ms' => ['Cuti Raya Aidilfitri (cuti umum).'], 'activities_en' => ['Hari Raya Aidilfitri public holiday.']],
            ], 'reflection_ms' => 'Minggu ini saya merangka struktur keseluruhan portal digital laporan latihan industri untuk laporan akhir latihan industri, termasuk migration untuk jadual portal_articles dan galleries. Saya juga membina pangkalan data MySQL bagi CMS dan portal serta membangunkan modul Pentadbiran Portal (Menus, Articles, Media) dalam CMS dengan konfigurasi routing Laravel. Pengalaman merancang seni bina maklumat dan menyelaraskan draf kandungan dengan panduan politeknik mengukuhkan kefahaman aliran laporan digital. Pengujian migration melalui rollback dan migrate semula turut mengajar ketelitian dalam definisi jenis data. Hari Jumaat adalah cuti Raya Aidilfitri. Secara keseluruhan, minggu ini meningkatkan keahlian pembangunan full-stack dan kepentingan struktur data yang sistematik untuk dokumentasi laporan yang profesional dan interaktif.', 'reflection_en' => 'This week I planned the overall industrial training report digital portal structure for the final industrial training report, including migrations for the portal_articles and galleries tables. I also built the MySQL database serving both the CMS and portal and developed the Portal Administration module (Menus, Articles, Media) inside the CMS with Laravel routing. Drafting information architecture and aligning content with the polytechnic guide strengthened how I structure a digital report. Working through migration errors using rollback and re-migrate taught me to be precise with column types. Friday was the Hari Raya Aidilfitri public holiday. Overall, this week improved my full-stack development skills and appreciation of systematic data structures for a professional, interactive final report.'],
            ['title_ms' => 'MINGGU 11', 'title_en' => 'WEEK 11', 'start_date' => '2026-03-23', 'end_date' => '2026-03-27', 'topic_ms' => 'Pembangunan halaman utama portal, modul pengenalan organisasi dan modul penghargaan', 'topic_en' => 'Development of portal home page, organizational introduction module and acknowledgement module', 'days' => [
                ['day_ms' => 'Isnin', 'day_en' => 'Monday', 'activities_ms' => ['Cuti Umum Hari Raya Aidilfitri.'], 'activities_en' => ['Public holiday for Hari Raya Aidilfitri.']],
                ['day_ms' => 'Selasa', 'day_en' => 'Tuesday', 'activities_ms' => ['Cuti Umum Hari Raya Aidilfitri.'], 'activities_en' => ['Public holiday for Hari Raya Aidilfitri.']],
                ['day_ms' => 'Rabu', 'day_en' => 'Wednesday', 'activities_ms' => ['Pembangunan halaman utama (Home) portal.', 'Bahan: laptop, VS Code, Laragon.', 'Membina antaramuka bagi paparan profil pelajar dan syarikat.', 'Membangunkan bahagian navigasi cepat untuk pautan terus ke modul laporan.', 'Mengintegrasikan data pangkalan data ke paparan halaman utama.'], 'activities_en' => ['Development of the portal home (Home) page.', 'Tools: laptop, VS Code, Laragon.', 'Built the interface for student and company profile display.', 'Developed the quick navigation section for direct links to report modules.', 'Integrated database data into the main page display.']],
                ['day_ms' => 'Khamis', 'day_en' => 'Thursday', 'activities_ms' => ['Pembangunan modul pengenalan organisasi.', 'Bahan: laptop, VS Code, Laragon.', 'Membangunkan halaman bagi sub-menu Pengenalan Diri dan Latar Belakang Organisasi.', 'Membangunkan paparan Objektif, Visi, Misi dan Carta Organisasi.', 'Menyiapkan kandungan Fungsi Bahagian serta Halatuju Organisasi dalam portal.'], 'activities_en' => ['Development of the organizational introduction module.', 'Tools: laptop, VS Code, Laragon.', 'Developed pages for Self-Introduction and Organizational Background sub-menus.', 'Built the display for Objectives, Vision, Mission, and Organizational Chart.', 'Finalized the content for Departmental Functions and Organizational Direction in the portal.']],
                ['day_ms' => 'Jumaat', 'day_en' => 'Friday', 'activities_ms' => ['Pembangunan modul penghargaan dan penyelarasan kandungan.', 'Bahan: laptop, VS Code, Laragon.', 'Membangunkan halaman Penghargaan untuk menghargai pihak syarikat dan keluarga.', 'Menyusun kandungan Ringkasan Eksekutif yang menjelaskan tugasan latihan industri.', 'Mengemaskini teks kandungan portal supaya selari dengan format laporan rasmi.'], 'activities_en' => ['Development of the acknowledgement module and content alignment.', 'Tools: laptop, VS Code, Laragon.', 'Developed the Acknowledgement page to appreciate the company and family.', 'Organized the Executive Summary content explaining industrial training tasks.', 'Updated the portal content text to align with the official report format.']],
            ], 'reflection_ms' => 'Minggu ini saya membangunkan antaramuka utama portal laporan akhir yang merangkumi profil peribadi dan navigasi pantas. Saya juga menyiapkan modul pengenalan organisasi serta kandungan penghargaan bagi melengkapkan komponen awal portal. Berjaya mengintegrasikan pangkalan data dengan paparan web secara dinamik menggunakan Laravel.', 'reflection_en' => 'This week I developed the main interface of the final report portal, including personal profiles and quick navigation. I also completed the organizational introduction module and acknowledgement content to finalize the portal\'s initial components. I successfully integrated the database with dynamic web displays using Laravel.'],
            ['title_ms' => 'MINGGU 12', 'title_en' => 'WEEK 12', 'start_date' => '2026-03-30', 'end_date' => '2026-04-03', 'topic_ms' => 'Pembangunan modul Ringkasan Aktiviti, Laporan Teknikal, Rumusan, Lampiran dan pengurusan data seeding minggu 1–11', 'topic_en' => 'Development of Activity Summary, Technical Report, Summary, Attachments modules and weeks 1–11 data seeding', 'days' => [
                ['day_ms' => 'Isnin', 'day_en' => 'Monday', 'activities_ms' => ['Pembangunan modul Ringkasan Aktiviti bagi portal laporan akhir.', 'Bahan: laptop, VS Code, Laragon.', 'Membina antaramuka untuk paparan log harian mengikut minggu.', 'Membangunkan senarai aktiviti dikategorikan mengikut minggu (Minggu 1 hingga Minggu 20).', 'Mengintegrasikan pangkalan data ke paparan portal dan menyusun jadual ringkasan tugas supaya kemas dan sistematik.', 'Menggunakan teknik penyusunan data yang cekap dalam Laravel supaya data banyak dipaparkan teratur tanpa menjejaskan prestasi portal.'], 'activities_en' => ['Development of the Activity Summary module for the final-report portal.', 'Tools: laptop, VS Code, Laragon.', 'Built the interface for daily logs grouped by week.', 'Developed the activity list grouped by week (Week 1 to Week 20).', 'Integrated the database into the portal display and organised the task summary table neatly.', 'Applied efficient Laravel data structuring so large activity lists stay orderly without hurting performance.']],
                ['day_ms' => 'Selasa', 'day_en' => 'Tuesday', 'activities_ms' => ['Pembangunan modul Laporan Teknikal portal.', 'Bahan: laptop, VS Code, Laragon.', 'Membangunkan antaramuka merangkumi pengenalan tugasan dan latar belakang projek.', 'Menyusun kemahiran teknikal Laravel langkah demi langkah (Migration, seeder, Model, Controller, route).', 'Melaksanakan paparan langkah teknikal berserta gambar rajah kod dan panggilan data.', 'Memastikan format teks dan susun atur gambar selari dengan standard dokumentasi teknikal; menyesuaikan saiz imej melalui lightbox atau had saiz responsif.'], 'activities_en' => ['Development of the portal Technical Report module.', 'Tools: laptop, VS Code, Laragon.', 'Built the interface covering task introduction and project background.', 'Organised Laravel technical skills step by step (Migration, seeder, Model, Controller, route).', 'Implemented step-by-step technical views with code figures and data calls.', 'Aligned text and figure layout with technical documentation standards; tuned image size using lightbox or responsive limits.']],
                ['day_ms' => 'Rabu', 'day_en' => 'Wednesday', 'activities_ms' => ['Pembangunan modul Rumusan portal laporan akhir.', 'Bahan: laptop, VS Code, Laragon.', 'Membangunkan antaramuka untuk paparan kesimpulan keseluruhan latihan industri.', 'Mengintegrasikan teks kesimpulan daripada pangkalan data supaya paparan bersifat dinamik.', 'Menggunakan grid CSS supaya kad pencapaian utama kekal responsif dan kemas pada skrin berbeza.'], 'activities_en' => ['Development of the Summary module for the final-report portal.', 'Tools: laptop, VS Code, Laragon.', 'Built the interface for the overall industrial training conclusion.', 'Integrated conclusion text from the database for dynamic display.', 'Used a CSS grid so key-achievement cards stay responsive and tidy across screen sizes.']],
                ['day_ms' => 'Khamis', 'day_en' => 'Thursday', 'activities_ms' => ['Pembangunan modul Lampiran portal laporan akhir.', 'Bahan: laptop, VS Code, Laragon.', 'Membangunkan antaramuka utama termasuk pengenalan dokumen sokongan.', 'Membina bahagian rujukan dengan pautan dokumentasi Laravel, Tailwind CSS, dan portal rasmi berkaitan; menetapkan `target="_blank"` untuk pautan luar.', 'Mengintegrasikan pengurusan media supaya imej boleh dikemas kini secara dinamik melalui pentadbiran portal.'], 'activities_en' => ['Development of the Attachments module for the final-report portal.', 'Tools: laptop, VS Code, Laragon.', 'Built the main interface including supporting-document introduction.', 'Added a references section with Laravel, Tailwind CSS, and related official links; set `target="_blank"` for external URLs.', 'Integrated media management so images can be updated dynamically via portal administration.']],
                ['day_ms' => 'Jumaat', 'day_en' => 'Friday', 'activities_ms' => ['Pengurusan data Ringkasan Aktiviti minggu 1 hingga 11 dan pembangunan database seeder.', 'Bahan: laptop, VS Code, Laragon, MySQL/SQL.', 'Mengumpul data harian dan mingguan, menyusun dalam format array untuk seeder.', 'Membangunkan fail seeder dan menjalankan `php artisan db:seed`.', 'Melakukan semakan silang bagi mengelakkan pertindihan atau pendua data.'], 'activities_en' => ['Managing Activity Summary data for weeks 1 through 11 and building the database seeder.', 'Tools: laptop, VS Code, Laragon, MySQL/SQL.', 'Collected daily and weekly records and structured them as arrays for the seeder.', 'Implemented the seeder file and ran `php artisan db:seed`.', 'Cross-checked entries to avoid overlapping or duplicate data.']],
            ], 'reflection_ms' => 'Minggu ini saya melengkapkan modul Ringkasan Aktiviti, Laporan Teknikal, Rumusan dan Lampiran bagi portal laporan akhir. Saya melaksanakan data seeding untuk memasukkan rekod aktiviti minggu 1 hingga 11 serta menyusun kandungan menggunakan elemen UI seperti kad dan grid. Berjaya mengurus pangkalan data berskala besar melalui seeder Laravel dan mendokumentasikan perjalanan latihan industri secara digital dengan lebih sistematik.', 'reflection_en' => 'This week I completed the Activity Summary, Technical Report, Summary, and Attachments modules for the final-report portal. I ran data seeding to load weeks 1 through 11 and organised content using UI elements such as cards and grids. I successfully managed larger datasets with Laravel seeders and documented the industrial training journey digitally in a more systematic way.'],
